author: Channel Awesome
description:
The Cinema Snob’s journey through 1964 IN FILM is here!  From the magical highs of Mary Poppins, to the award winning My Fair Lady, to The Beatles having a Hard Day’s Night, all the way to the gold covered thrills of Goldfinger, and most importantly, Santa Claus conquering some Martians. 

It’s all the classics, forgotten oddities, cult favorites, and even some misfires that defined the year.
